---
---

<section id="faq" class="py-24 bg-tech-darker">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        Frequently Asked <span class="text-tech-accent">Questions</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400">
        Got questions? We've got answers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
      <div class="bg-tech-card border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pr-8">What areas do you serve?</h3>
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            We serve the entire Denver Metro area including Denver, Aurora, Lakewood, Littleton, Centennial, Highlands Ranch, and Boulder. Travel within 25 miles of downtown Denver is included in our rates.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <div class="bg-tech-card border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pr-8">Do you offer emergency services?</h3>
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            Yes! We offer 24/7 emergency support for critical issues like security breaches, complete network outages, or smart home lockouts. Emergency calls have an additional $150 fee but we prioritize getting you back up and running fast.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <div class="bg-tech-card border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pr-8">What smart home brands do you work with?</h3>
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            We work with all major brands including Ring, Nest, Philips Hue, Lutron, Ecobee, August, Yale, and many more. We're brand-agnostic—we recommend what works best for your needs and budget, not what gives us the best commission.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <div class="bg-tech-card border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pr-8">Do you offer warranties?</h3>
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            All our work comes with a 90-day warranty. If something we installed or configured stops working within 90 days, we'll fix it free of charge. Hardware warranties are handled through manufacturers, but we'll help you navigate those claims.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 5 -->
      <div class="bg-tech-card border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pr-8">Can you work with existing equipment?</h3>
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            Absolutely! We'll work with what you have and integrate new equipment where needed. We'll tell you honestly if something should be replaced versus repaired. No pressure to buy new gear unless it actually makes sense.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 6 -->
      <div class="bg-tech-card border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pr-8">Do I need to be home during the service?</h3>
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            For most services, yes—we'll need access and want to walk you through what we did. However, for businesses or repeat clients, we can arrange secure access. We'll always verify the work with you before considering it complete.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 7 -->
      <div class="bg-tech-card border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pr-8">What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            We accept all major credit cards, debit cards, Venmo, PayPal, and checks. For business clients, we offer Net-30 terms with approved credit. Payment is due at time of service unless arranged otherwise.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
